<div class="ff-container">
  <!-- Header & Actions -->
  <div class="ff-header">
    <div class="ff-title">
      <h3>⚙️ 功能开关 (Feature Flags)</h3>
      <p>管理 <code>xhunt_config</code>, 控制测试功能对特定用户的可见性。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ff-actions">
      <button id="ff-reload-btn" class="btn secondary">🔄 Reload</button>
      <button id="ff-publish-btn" class="btn primary">🚀 Publish</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Tab Navigation -->
  <div class="ff-tabs-nav">
    <button class="ff-tab-btn active" data-tab="flexible">
      灵活测试 (Flexible)
    </button>
    <button class="ff-tab-btn" data-tab="test">测试组 (Test)</button>
    <button class="ff-tab-btn" data-tab="canary">金丝雀 (Canary)</button>
  </div>

  <!-- Tab Content -->
  <div class="ff-tabs-content">
    <!-- Flexible Testing Tab -->
    <div class="ff-tab-pane active" id="ff-tab-flexible">
      <p class="ff-tab-desc">
        <b>最高优先级：</b> 在这里定义的功能，其用户名单将覆盖下方 Test 和
        Canary 组的同名功能配置。
      </p>
      <div id="ff-flexible-list" class="ff-flexible-list"></div>
      <button id="ff-add-flexible-btn" class="btn add-rule-btn">
        + 添加灵活规则
      </button>
    </div>

    <!-- Test Config Tab -->
    <div class="ff-tab-pane" id="ff-tab-test">
      <p class="ff-tab-desc">
        <b>中等优先级：</b> 功能在这里定义后，只有 Testers
        列表中的用户可见。若同一功能也存在于 Flexible Testing
        中，则此处的配置被忽略。
      </p>
      <div class="ff-card compact">
        <div class="ff-field">
          <label>Test Features</label>
          <div id="ff-test-features" class="tag-input-container"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="ff-field">
          <details class="ff-collapsible-list">
            <summary>
              <label>Testers</label>
              <span class="user-count"></span>
            </summary>
            <div id="ff-test-testers" class="tag-input-container large"></div>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Canary Config Tab -->
    <div class="ff-tab-pane" id="ff-tab-canary">
      <p class="ff-tab-desc">
        <b>最低优先级：</b> 功能在这里定义后，只有 Canaries
        列表中的用户可见。若同一功能也存在于 Flexible 或 Test
        中，则此处的配置被忽略。
      </p>
      <div class="ff-card compact">
        <div class="ff-field">
          <label>Canary Features</label>
          <div id="ff-canary-features" class="tag-input-container"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="ff-field">
          <details class="ff-collapsible-list">
            <summary>
              <label>Canaries</label>
              <span class="user-count"></span>
            </summary>
            <div
              id="ff-canary-canaries"
              class="tag-input-container large"
            ></div>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Feature Keys Reference -->
  <div class="ff-reference-card">
    <details>
      <summary>查看所有可用的功能键 (Feature Keys)</summary>
      <div id="ff-keys-list" class="ff-keys-list"></div>
    </details>
  </div>

  <div class="ff-toast" id="ff-toast" style="display: none"></div>

  <!-- Diff Modal -->
  <div id="ff-diff-modal" class="ff-modal" style="display: none">
    <div class="ff-modal-content">
      <div class="ff-modal-header">
        <h4>Review Changes</h4>
        <span id="ff-diff-modal-close" class="close-btn">&times;</span>
      </div>
      <div class="ff-modal-body">
        <p>
          Please review your changes before publishing.
          <span class="legend-added">Added</span> |
          <span class="legend-removed">Removed</span>
        </p>
        <pre id="ff-diff-output"></pre>
      </div>
      <div class="ff-modal-footer">
        <button id="ff-diff-cancel-btn" class="btn secondary">Cancel</button>
        <button id="ff-diff-confirm-btn" class="btn primary">
          Confirm & Publish
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

